### Register a new user
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "vusumzi",
  "password": "secret123",
  "role": "ROLE_USER"
}

###

### Login (extract token for later use)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "vusumzi",
  "password": "secret123"
}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.token); %}

###

### Create content (requires token)
POST {{host}}/api/contents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My first post",
  "desc": "Learning Spring Boot with JWT",
  "status": "DRAFT"
}

###

### Get all contents
GET {{host}}/api/contents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get content by ID
GET {{host}}/api/contents/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update content
PUT {{host}}/api/contents/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated post",
  "desc": "This is now published",
  "status": "PUBLISHED"
}

###

### Delete content
DELETE {{host}}/api/contents/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
